data.description: Welcome to your dream home located in the beautiful Nottingham Country! This stunning 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath home has been completely renovated to meet all your needs. The kitchen is a chef's dream featuring undermount cabinet lighting, black stainless steel appliances, double ovens, and ample counter space to create your culinary masterpieces. The spacious living room is perfect for gatherings or entertaining guests. Need a home office? We've got you covered with a dedicated space for your work-from-home needs. Plus, the bonus room offers additional flexible living space to create the perfect playroom, game room, or home gym. Step outside and enjoy the professionally landscaped yard complete with a sparkling swimming pool, perfect for those hot summer days. This home is perfect for anyone looking for both comfort and luxury. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this your forever home. This home has tons of upgrades!  Come and see it today
